This paper is primarily focused on face alignment, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new approach using a mixture of experts with tree-structured gates, which involves machine learning techniques such as regression and deep learning. Therefore, it is likely to also fall under sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural networks (cs.NE).
